This software is the reference implementation of the **MORPHEUS** methodology —
**M**emory **O**vernight **R**e-parameterization, **P**romotion via **H**eld-out
**E**val, **U**pdate **S**napshots — a system for nightly LoRA consolidation of
agent memories into language model weights. The MORPHEUS methodology was
originated and first published by Mr Dula Solutions on 2026-05-26 in this
repository.

The relationship between project and methodology:
  - DreamAgent  = the project / repository / CLI / reference implementation
  - MORPHEUS    = the methodology DreamAgent implements

